oai_dc:dc.dc:title: White Stores - Unidentified group

oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Unidentified seated group, mostly men. Ordered by White Stores. Submitted ID: on far back row: man with no tie is Harry McDonald (1903-1944; man two places to the right with big smile is Dwight McDonald (1907-1975), president 1953-1975; Man one further to the right with glasses is Frank McDonald (1870-1953), founder and president.
